title: "Persian Suite No. 1 (&quot;Nava&quot;)"
instrumentation: tar &amp; string quintet
category_music: Chamber Ensemble
year_composed: 2022
duration: 15'
tags:
 - Iranian Culture
---
This four-movement suite for tar (traditional Iranian instrument) and string quintet is inspired by a mode of Persian classical music called "Nava," known for its spiritual and meditative qualities.